Nutrient data for: TERRY'S CHOCOLATE ORANGE SEGSATIONS CHOCOLATE AND CANDY PIECES MIXED, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210286550
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, dried skimmed MILK, dried whey (from MILK), vegetable fats (palm, shea), MILK fat, rice flour, emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin, E476, E471), glucose syrup, flavourings, salt, lactose (from MILK). MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.COCOA SOLIDS 25% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER.  NUTS, WHEAT.
